					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The problem looks like you are just sticking pieces of code next to each other without regard to what's actually going on.
<br />Specifically, you are letting the program counter run from the boot-up code into the VRAM copy code, and then that returns (RTS instruction).  So you didn't call it (no JSR instruction), so it returns to 0000 at the end since there's no return address on the stack.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
