				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You're messing with the memory clear loop for no good reason, making it clear some ram to 00, then the rest of the ram to FE.  Use two separate loops to clear your sprite table memory to FE and the rest of memory to 00.
<br />
<br />But that's not causing your problem.
<br />You are copying 32 bytes from a source with only 16 bytes.  Of course the other 16 bytes will be unrelated crap that doesn't look like normal sprites.</div>

					
