					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Dah, must have been a relic from my unrolled CPX $4016 version where you DID need to invert the bits.  (and I was thinking of the GBA too...)
<br />Sorry, bits rotated out of 4016 and rotated back into the variable do not need to be inverted.
<br />
<br />Here's the actual code I use for joypad reading...
